reviewText: What the hell happened after the first film  was good. This isn't the worst movie I've ever seen,but the entire cast just seems to be going through the motions. The heart of the first film is just really missing. I hate how they replaced the original actors of half dead and seldom seen with dudes I didn't care about. This film could have been so much better.
summary: horrible stay away from this film with no heart.
